{"title":"方程的解","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":0,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-5652","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>小哈最近遇到了一个新的问题。</p><p>对于x1 + x2 + x3 + .... + xm = n 这个方程中。</p><p>如果每个xi都满足</p><p>0 &lt;= xi &lt;= val</p><p>那么这个方程的解的个数是多少个呢?</p><p><br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>输入有三个数字，</p><p>n、m、val如题目所述</p><p>题目是多case的，请处理到文件结束</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>一行代表一个答案。</p><p>由于答案可能很大，请输出其模（1e9 + 7）后的值</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>6    2     4<br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>3</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>n &lt;= 1e14</p><p>m &lt;= 1000</p><p>val &lt;= 1e14</p><p><br></p><p>对于第一个样例，其答案是</p><p>2   4</p><p>3   3</p><p>4   2</p><p>所以答案是3</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}